Package inspiracio.servlet.http

Class Summary
ETag Methods for managing ETag.
HttpURL A JavaBean for a complete URL for http and https.
 

Exception Summary
BadRequestException A method called within an http request signals that the response to the request should be 400 Bad request.
ForbiddenException A method called within an http request signals that the response to the request should be 403 Forbidden.
HttpException A method called from within an http request signals that the response should be an error response, with status code like 4** or 5**:
InternalServerErrorException A method called within an http request signals that the response should be 500 Internal Server Error.
MethodNotAllowedException Status code (405) indicating that the method specified in the Request-Line is not allowed for the resource identified by the Request-URI.
NotAuthorizedException A method called within an http request signals that the response should be 401 Not Authorized.
NotFoundException A method called within an http request signals that the response to the request should be 404 Not found.
PreconditionFailedException A method called within an http request signals that the response should be 412 Precondition Failed.
